headline: Trump's Election Caused a Sell-Off in Clean Energy Stocks. But Is It an Opportunity for These 2 Industry Leaders?
summary: Trump's election has caused renewable and electric vehicle (EV) stocks to crash. But these industry leaders could be bargains.
